sekt.sem:
The pb/ tag marks a page break in the copy-text or other editions of the text;
     in the latter case edRef gives the edition in question.
     The milestone tag marks a journal entry for edRef="#Pap." n="volumesectionnumber"; entries not present in that edition is given the attribute unit="unnumbered", se example in . The element also applies to letters in edRef="#BogA", see example in .

